Write a program to add all the elements in the array and print the final value?

********************************************************************************
public class Add_All_Elements {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int [] a= new int[] {1,2,3,4,5};
		int sum =0;
		for(int i =0;i<a.length;i++)
		{
			sum=sum+a[i];	
		}
		System.out.println("Sum of all the element of the array:"+sum);
	}
}
********************************************************************************
